OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FSharlene Rochard, Liz Stein, and
OL,8,FDanielle Bensky say they were sexually
OL,9,Fabused by Jeffrey Epstein. This week,
OL,10,Fthey have travelled to the UK to ask
OL,11,Ffor more to be done to hold those in
OL,12,Fpower to account
OL,14,FWarning: There are details in this
OL,15,Fstory that some people may find
OL,16,Fdistressing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/22
