OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FSurvivors of Jeffrey Epstein have said
OL,8,Fthe UK is "setting the standard" when
OL,9,Fit comes to holding people who appear
OL,10,Fin the Epstein files to account, while
OL,11,Fin the US there is "a lack of
OL,12,Fmotivation" to get justice for victims.
OL,14,FSharlene Rochard, Liz Stein, and
OL,15,FDanielle Bensky say they were sexually
OL,16,Fassaulted by Epstein and have
OL,17,Ftravelled to the UK to speak to
OL,18,FBritish MPs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
