CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773331878
OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FThey are calling on Peter Mandelson,
OL,8,FAndrew Mountbatten Windsor, and other
OL,9,Fpeople in positions of power to
OL,10,Fprovide evidence about the convicted
OL,11,Fpaedophile.
OL,13,FSharlene, who was abused by Epstein
OL,14,Ffor around a decade, having been
OL,15,Fintroduced to him when she was 16 or
OL,16,F17 years old, told Good Morning
OL,17,FBritain on Wednesday that while
OL,18,Fsurvivors "appreciate" that MPs are
OL,19,F"taking this seriously", they also
OL,20,Fneed to put pressure on the US to have
OL,21,Fmore people provide evidence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
