CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773331878
OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FPeople who remained friends with
OL,8,FEpstein after his conviction, such as
OL,9,FPeter Mandelson and Andrew Mountbatten
OL,10,FWindsor, "need to stand up and be
OL,11,Fcompletely transparent with what had
OL,12,Fhappened and show accountability", she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"We want accountability, we want
OL,16,Ftransparency," she added.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/22
