OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FDanielle Bensky, who was 17 year old
OL,8,Fwhen she met Epstein, said the UK
OL,9,F"does seem to be setting the standard"
OL,10,Fon the Epstein files, and that the
OL,11,FUnited States needs to be doing more.
OL,13,F"The rest of the world does seem to be
OL,14,Ffollowing suit, except for the US...
OL,15,F(We're) not sure why we're not seeing
OL,16,Fthe level of accountability that we
OL,17,Fneed to, but it's why we desperately
OL,18,Fneed investigations into what is in
OL,19,Fthe files."
OL,26,@wD@ApmwD@Gpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
