OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FMore than three million pages of
OL,8,Fdocuments, including over 2,000 videos
OL,9,Fand 180,000 images, were released by
OL,10,Fthe US Justice Department in February,
OL,11,Fmaking up a large part of the so-
OL,12,Fcalled Epstein files.
OL,14,FWhile there have been arrests and
OL,15,Finvestigations as a result of the
OL,16,Frelease, much of the information in
OL,17,Fthe files remains a mystery due to
OL,18,Fheavy redactions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
