OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FLast month, Lord Peter Mandelson was
OL,8,Fsummoned by the United States Congress
OL,9,Fto answer questions about his
OL,10,Frelationship with Epstein. He has
OL,11,Fconsistently denied any knowledge of
OL,12,FEpstein's crimes and has denied all
OL,13,Fwrongdoing.
OL,15,FAndrew has also denied any wrongdoing
OL,16,Fover his links to the convicted sex
OL,17,Foffender.
OL,19,FEpstein died before his trial, meaning
OL,20,Fthat most survivors were unable to go
OL,21,Fto court against him directly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
