OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FSharlene Rochard: "It's not always up
OL,8,Fto survivors to come forward"
OL,10,FSharlene said it should not be the
OL,11,Fresponsibility of survivors to fill in
OL,12,Fthose blanks, and while she is not
OL,13,Fnecessarily able to give as many
OL,14,Fdetails as she can because she is
OL,15,Fvulnerable, there are many other
OL,16,Fpeople who would be able to give
OL,17,Fevidence that have not yet come
OL,18,Fforward.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
