PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773331878
OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,F"It's not always up to survivors to
OL,8,Fcome forward and say things that we
OL,9,Fknow. Everybody was there, these were
OL,10,Fbig events, lots of people were there.
OL,12,F"There are a lot of different things
OL,13,Fthat I have been through because I was
OL,14,Ftravelling as a model... Depending on
OL,15,Fwhere you were, Jeffrey would say
OL,16,F'maybe you would want to meet
OL,17,Fsomebody.'"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
