OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FSharlene was asked to go to Epstein's
OL,8,FNew York apartment, to Florida, and to
OL,9,Fhis island, and she was "forced to do
OL,10,Fthings of (a) sexual nature with him".
OL,11,FShe was 16 or 17 at the time, and the
OL,12,Fage of consent in New York and Florida
OL,13,Fis 18.
OL,15,FDanielle Bensky: "It was systematic
OL,16,Fand it was manipulative"
OL,26,@rD@KpmrD@Mpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
