OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773331878
OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FDanielle Bensky was a dancer when she
OL,8,Fwas recruited by another girl to spend
OL,9,Ftime with the disgraced financier, and
OL,10,Fshe was drawn in by the idea that she
OL,11,Fcould earn money while continuing to
OL,12,Fdance.
OL,14,FShe said she had agreed to do massage
OL,15,Fwork, but had not agreed to any sexual
OL,16,Factivity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773331878
OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,F"There was a grooming tactic... It was
OL,8,Fsystematic and it was manipulative.
OL,9,FThe first time that I went, it was
OL,10,Fjust a massage and he would talk to me
OL,11,Fabout dance... the things my peers
OL,12,Fnever wanted to talk about.
OL,14,FHe then would say that he dated famous
OL,15,Fballet dancers "who loved to get
OL,16,Fnaked" and that Danielle "should try
OL,17,Fthat".
OL,19,FDanielle said Epstein's hold over her
OL,20,Fbecame more powerful when her mother
OL,21,Fbecame ill.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773331878
OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FWhen Danielle's mother was diagnosed
OL,8,Fwith a rare brain tumour, Epstein
OL,9,Fsuggested that he could help her, but
OL,10,Fonly if Danielle either recruited more
OL,11,Fgirls or she "would do more". She
OL,12,Fnever recruited anyone else and said
OL,13,Fthe "tone shifted" when she next saw
OL,14,Fhim.
OL,16,F"The mental manipulation was worse -
OL,17,Fsurvivors are not a monolith,
OL,18,Feverybody has their own story but in
OL,19,Fmy case it was the mental gymnastics
OL,20,Fthat were always in play. I just felt
OL,21,Fthat I was so stuck," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773331878
OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,F"We have to stop letting power exploit
OL,8,Fthe vulnerable across the board... and
OL,9,Fit's really on display in these
OL,10,Ffiles... It is really about if anybody
OL,11,Fin any position of power knows
OL,12,Fanything, they need to speak... We
OL,13,Fcan't just keep going at this rate. At
OL,14,Fsome point there needs to be some
OL,15,Fbravery from within."
OL,17,FLiz Stein: "The fear I felt seemed to
OL,18,Ffuel them"
OL,20,FLiz Stein was 21 when she was
OL,21,Fapproached by Maxwell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773331878
OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,F"Their pursuit of me really felt like
OL,8,Fa game. From my initial meeting with
OL,9,Fthem all of the alarm bells inside of
OL,10,Fme were going off. Even though I knew
OL,11,Fthere was something really scary about
OL,12,Fthem that I needed to avoid, the
OL,13,Femotional manipulation... Traffickers
OL,14,Fdon't come up to you and say 'hi, we
OL,15,Fwant to traffic you'. It's a very slow
OL,16,Fand manipulative process of grooming,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773331878
OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FShe was isolated from friends and
OL,8,Ffamily and work colleagues, leaving
OL,9,Fher "entirely dependent" on Epstein
OL,10,Fand Maxwell.
OL,12,F"You feel like you have really no
OL,13,Fother option other than to placate
OL,14,Fthem, to give them what they're asking
OL,15,Fof you, because you really don't have
OL,16,Fanyone to turn to."
OL,18,FLiz went as far as to move apartments,
OL,19,Fchange cities, and eventually leave
OL,20,Fthe state to try to get away from
OL,21,FEpstein and Maxwell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31519
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773331878
OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,F"The fear that I felt ... it seemed to
OL,8,Ffuel them. They seemed to be excited
OL,9,Fby how terrified I was."
OL,11,FAnd if people were to ask her why she
OL,12,Fdidn't just leave, Liz said: "I
OL,13,Fcertainly tried."
OL,15,FShe only managed to stop what was
OL,16,Fhappening when she suffered a nervous
OL,17,Fbreakdown, she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
