OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1773331878
OL,3,CEpstein files: Survivors say UK
OL,4,C'setting the standard' with
OL,5,Cinvestigations
OL,7,FCabinet minister Darren Jones said a
OL,8,F"big number" of the documents will be
OL,9,Freleased, although it is only expected
OL,10,Fto be a fraction of the papers
OL,11,Fdemanded by Parliament.
OL,13,FLast month, MPs ordered the government
OL,14,Fto release tens of thousands of
OL,15,Fdocuments relating to Lord Mandelson's
OL,16,Fappointment in 2024 after questions
OL,17,Fover how the peer was vetted, plus
OL,18,Fwhat was known about his links to
OL,19,FEpstein.
